（2）Access  ocean.accentrix.com (If you don't want to change the hosts file, you can access http://192.168.118.115 or http://192.168.118.113  directly)






3.Visit Kuboard

Access http://192.168.118.113:32567/



#先找到所有kuboard 的secret ,一般是在包含system 的namespace 下面

kubectl -n kube-system get secret |grep kuboard


#然后再describe kuboard-user-token-xxx 的sercret

kubectl -n kube-system describe secret kuboard-user-token-rwsws
